Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類因人口膨脹而向宇宙移民已過了半個世紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周圍漂浮著巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為人類的「第二故鄉」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們就在這裏出生、成長、生兒育女\N並走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世紀0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離地球最遠的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.49,0:02:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公國之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球聯邦政府發起了獨立戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在開始一個月的戰鬥里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.35,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國和地球聯邦軍有半數以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們對於自己的行為產生了恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『核心戰鬥機逃脫命令』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，病人的情況如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.33,0:03:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,107號室正常！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.13,0:03:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.04,0:03:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嗎？大家好嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈囉，靜一點好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公公，來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，這裏一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.00,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.92,0:03:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，若有事的話請告訴我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，引擎有少許故障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪速度有百分之八的差距出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.16,0:03:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以再減百分之十二衝力來計算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.04,0:03:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看要進入衛星軌道有很大困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.17,0:03:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該可以和那邊線路接通的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彈射線的堅程度如何...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.65,0:03:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不必擔心了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彈射線本來是給GUNDAM用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以核戰機應該沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.19,0:03:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.96,0:04:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有責任去保護百姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.13,0:04:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果母艦放下難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可以回衛星軌道等候命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是ZION軍的佔領區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可就此放下他們呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放難民在這裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長的意思是要周圍逃避吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有這樣想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有說錯嗎？你要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糧食怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦上有近百人是不能作戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才這位年輕人說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這班人都是被聯邦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強迫往宇宙移民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經過千辛萬苦才來到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻不可著陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是死不瞑目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們大家的心情也和我相同嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.61,0:04:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我現在有個好辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以用母艦的彈射系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.35,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將核戰機飛彈出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當飛離敵人進入彈道軌道後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可以和聯邦軍聯絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說的可能性很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也計算過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！只要將彈射線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接入主要引擎的蒸氣管內就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是沒問題的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，米萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些難民發生了騷亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請立即來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看大家一直和敵人比耐性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.71,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就沒用！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如照提議試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題是杜林線的接駁是否可行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.98,0:05:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.82,0:05:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有誰可抵抗發射的反衝擊力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是由我提案的，就讓我去做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使失敗也有我做犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.89,0:05:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？真有膽識呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次的事亦未必是一定失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.13,0:05:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特隊長，快著手改裝彈射器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為如何，李中尉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.54,0:05:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是和參謀本部聯絡為首要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.18,0:06:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有GUNDAM數據送來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！收集到的都送來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真叫人吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單從外表觀察推算出來的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已和我們的機動戰士有天淵之別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.93,0:06:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果還收集到內部結構就好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.83,0:06:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！你竟然對著這種機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還可追跡了二日的時間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.07,0:06:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪，我也費了很大的氣力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不難明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔，我們不可再花時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以在15分鐘內就改好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.55,0:06:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不太難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要將主引擎的動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒸氣管接入去就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，快些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先吃點東西吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別吃太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！我在吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.50,0:06:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最初的30秒是十分痛苦的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.63,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！那些難民發生暴動了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暴動？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.83,0:06:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那班老人將小琪他們捉去做人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要求White Base降落到地面呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.51,0:07:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再吃了，會嘔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.92,0:07:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.81,0:07:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.91,0:07:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波認為小琪他們既幼小又可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經自願成為人質了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.12,0:07:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在核戰機內有多少駕駛時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有模擬的18小時...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訓練35小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實戰2小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你的經驗是那麼淺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法了，那麼只有加油吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.74,0:07:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不擔心的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好的朋友芙勞·波被捉去做人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.94,0:07:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道一點也不擔心嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，這裏有隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊、雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.18,0:07:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.31,0:07:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為有他們處理一定沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在只可做自己能力範圍內的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅說得沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去發射部份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你出去後要有心理準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION一定會追蹤而來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.43,0:08:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.14,0:08:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幸災樂禍嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹嗎在大發脾氣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不過想忠告一下你便是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知！我是個沒出息的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的說話根本不值得你動怒啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的說話要有分寸呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.11,0:08:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，敵軍有行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎在調整高度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.34,0:08:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快和基地聯絡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.06,0:08:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校，剛才巡邏機有通信過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說他們有所行動了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快將資料送來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.35,0:08:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,計算機計出來的數據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.09,0:09:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞，你認為如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們可能想向衛星軋道方面逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.19,0:09:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但速度不吻合呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！難道他們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快！給我聯絡杜力中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派小型戰機過來接我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞，這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬方面一定是想和聯邦軍接洽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.31,0:09:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報告他們被孤立的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始倒數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅準備...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,10、9、8、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.78,0:09:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,7、6、5、4、3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.79,0:09:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2、1、0...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.14,0:09:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機進入發射軌道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.51,0:09:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們發射了什麼出去呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.18,0:09:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否進入了軌道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.84,0:09:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想跳出包圍網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後和聯邦軍聯絡呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基地上空已佈滿粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.82,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他們不能使用雷達的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在該怎辦呢？夏亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祇好追啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還趕得及！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.66,0:10:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會在2分鐘後截到它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.36,0:10:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.46,0:10:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沒變呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳達命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為夏亞掩護！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.35,0:10:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經將全部情況告訴他們，但
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不想使用武力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也只想知事實的真相罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不應捉來人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家收回手槍...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.37,0:10:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收回手槍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.70,0:10:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我可回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想見見我的孫兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.81,0:11:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也只想看看小時候的故鄉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我丈夫還未死，我想再見他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.19,0:11:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒說不降落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.95,0:11:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你可以坦白告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.19,0:11:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有多久才可降落地面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然一切工作由你們負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.33,0:11:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我們為了平等地交涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不得不要他們陪同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.27,0:11:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知我們也是盡了全力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，請快到控制室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之快來吧！快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，可以恢復聯絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是控制室，請答話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請答話！核戰機！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.45,0:11:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅可能已經震死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別再胡鬧，好嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.56,0:11:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！\N有敵人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追蹤核戰機的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.23,0:11:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一分鐘後就會追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.04,0:12:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夏亞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.54,0:12:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那便糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.71,0:12:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！   請回答！   阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是White Base，請回答...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.51,0:12:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有多久才可追上？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大約30秒左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.28,0:12:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.08,0:12:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否被發現了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅仍未有回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.72,0:12:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去掩護阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.82,0:12:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火箭已準備好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊！我們盡速趕去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.52,0:12:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要沿著核戰機的路經！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.89,0:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主引擎最大戰速，去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷達不可用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.60,0:13:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有百分之三十的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.13,0:13:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球上粒子濃度太高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉強可以看到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要試試嗎？隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射吧！用陽動作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有火箭來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.08,0:13:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們射的根本不可能瞄得中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續接近吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.59,0:13:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會射中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.03,0:13:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.96,0:13:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你怎樣了！阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.26,0:13:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，請你答話，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.57,0:13:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你醒了嗎？阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.41,0:13:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敵戰機急速接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要鎮定啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杜力，這瞄準器不准啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，別被擊中！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎？要先看清楚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.53,0:14:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！要看清楚對方...沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方只是一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.67,0:14:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突入大氣層用的艦載機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是空戰用的戰鬥機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了，夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被擊中了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.20,0:14:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是致命傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,垂直下降吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.80,0:14:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼母艦仍不來掩護我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火箭為什麼不作掩護射擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.30,0:14:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為阿姆羅正夾在中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.51,0:14:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉強發射的話會打中核戰機的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.49,0:15:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,6對1我是沒可能嬴的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體人員準備對空攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅快回來White Base！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，回來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要保持冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡量靠近地面飛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.46,0:15:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是布萊特和李中尉的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還想逞強嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.34,0:15:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有做錯什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.07,0:15:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若果你仍然以這種態度的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.94,0:15:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算在宇宙我一樣會把你掟出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了...隊長...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.55,0:15:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機回來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.02,0:15:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎放棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各戰機，別讓他逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.76,0:15:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杜力，支持得住嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.07,0:15:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.64,0:15:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡烏正趕來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放出戰機，在空中決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.91,0:16:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了，是White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機已進入母艦火力範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.39,0:16:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快讓核戰機回來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM預備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有信心用GUNDAM在空中對付他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空中戰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.11,0:16:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但GUNDAM只是陸戰用的兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的，只要用自然降落法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會有1分鐘停留在空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.15,0:16:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的話一定可以做得到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.61,0:16:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳只是說當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼困難的事我沒信心做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.38,0:16:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是要生存下去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，快回White Base吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.79,0:16:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧！沒法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊，開始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開母艦特別門，快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備降落，完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.31,0:17:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改變操縱線路...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.04,0:17:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...可以做到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.18,0:17:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是沒有人有信心才會去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.42,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過阿姆羅，你是有才能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要打開特別門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人機動戰士出來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用ZAKU去應戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將艦載機升到敵艦上空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.83,0:18:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZAKU下來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.38,0:18:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？夏亞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.82,0:18:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,落地面前1分20秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要打倒他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這班傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.69,0:19:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球內用自然降落法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.92,0:19:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是一般人可以做得到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死人！GUNDAM竟在前面阻住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你們幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等...等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們又想做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是不能降落了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我們下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.71,0:19:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求求你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.25,0:19:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心，先回房去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，請先回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.93,0:19:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何我們是不會走的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除非能讓我們下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！激光槍的能源沒有了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不成，阿姆羅 先撤退吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被近距離擊中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝甲不一定支持得住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.18,0:20:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用火力掩護你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心炮彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.45,0:20:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這木馬...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！聽到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你對聯邦的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.49,0:20:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有必要再重新估計再定作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在由計算機的推算所得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.23,0:20:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵機動戰士是以戰鬥機為中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以自由變換形式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多用途機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.53,0:20:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.07,0:20:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！這豈不是說我一直所見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.87,0:21:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是白色機動戰士的部份威力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.24,0:21:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那以後怎樣應付呢？卡爾瑪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.68,0:21:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先回來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.75,0:21:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起研究！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.59,0:21:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別理他們，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.30,0:21:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要杯茶嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.35,0:21:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位小朋友..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.94,0:21:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又或者是在這裏的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都盡了力去戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.91,0:21:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點我是體會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.94,0:21:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我們都老了..無能為力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只想回地球去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.02,0:21:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點我是明白的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如就讓我們就在此地離艦吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還差一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.46,0:21:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可進入聯邦軍的領地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.06,0:21:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你們不再耐心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.19,0:21:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你可以保證我們的生命嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.76,0:21:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只希望我的兒子可以平安！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.17,0:22:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是只要一點時間就可降落嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.67,0:22:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們祇會為自己設想的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.97,0:22:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又怎會瞭解我們的心情呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.21,0:22:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.08,0:22:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是否只為了自己而去戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.28,0:22:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是為了大家才去拚命戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.95,0:22:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不想再做下去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.72,0:22:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.55,0:22:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先喝杯茶吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.86,0:22:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你將芙勞·波和那班小孩送回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.16,0:22:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們都全靠你了！小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.77,0:22:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.31,0:22:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,橫過山脈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.27,0:22:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.75,0:22:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祇好以山脈作屏障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.21,0:22:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正向著海面進發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.08,0:22:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祇好這樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.42,0:23:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓難民降落而停戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.29,0:23:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是趁這空隙卻已經在為下一場戰鬥佈陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.84,0:23:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而佩露西亞母子在他們所要歸去的大地上\N所看到的是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.69,0:23:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.31,0:23:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 『荒野是戰場』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.29,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠存活下去嗎？

